Avenda is exhibiting at the Summer Exhibition Shaldon, Devon, UK at the Victoria Hall 16 to 27 August 2018 (The Visit, Hot Air and Green Flowers 2

She will also be exhibiting at the Pavilions, Teignmouth, Devon, UK in support of The Cause, a new play by Dreadnaught South West about the suffrage campaign by Emmiline Pankhurst and Millicent Fawcett. The exhibition will be from 24 - 28 September 2018. (The Corsets are Off and they are Not going Back On).
